[I] Regulatory database used by Linux

[T] This repository contains the regulatory database file maintained for use
[T] with Central Regulatory Database Agent daemon.

[U] https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/wens/wireless-regdb.git

[A] John W. Linville
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/tool
[F] CROSS

[L] ISC
[V] 2026-05-30

[D] 2c351146d382bb4787de42f297a6c48be4a20d8a017283ab5d50edf4 wireless-regdb-master-2026-05-30.tar.gz https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/wens/wireless-regdb.git/snapshot/

runmake=0

hook_add postmake 5 "cp -fv regulatory.{db,db.p7s} $root/lib/firmware/"
